title: 'On the bottom left side of the image, standing on its hind legs, a tiny mouse looks diagonally out across a sunny landscape: desert, forests, mountains, cities and roads, the sea in the distance to one side. Amid a few wispy cirrus clouds hanga a small, strange red and green alien planet. Near the mouse are three tiny objects: a single sea shell, a single penny, and a single mushroom.'
pid: 8a918f36-a81e-4f85-ab18-143730c9f090
